data.description: This charming, secluded yet conveniently located, fenced and cross fenced 7-acre ranchette has it all.  Beautifully up-dated 4-bedroom home with family room plus office includes all new energy-efficient windows and patio doors installed in 2018.  Chain link fenced yard with towering shade trees.  Out-buildings to include a metal goat barn, chicken coop, duck coop, storage shed and a metal equipment shed with overhead door.  Current owners have replaced much of the fencing with four square fence topped with barbed wire and added the custom powder-coated solar powered entry gate with heavy duty opener and untreated cedar raised garden beds There is a seasonal creek on the property.  Water is supplied by Kempner water, and there is an old well of unknown condition on the property.  Septic tank was pumped and inspected 9-8-23.  The Polaris Ranger is for sale separately for $15,000. Hurry!
